    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior remains in pristine, original condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history; it drives exactly as it did when new. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or an enthusiast to own a truly exceptional example that requires absolutely nothing.",
